videos.headline: Baylor's Williams makes incredible interception
videos.description: Iowa State's Brock Purdy tries to throw the ball away, but Jordan Williams snags it while almost out of bounds.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play ( Baylor's Williams makes incredible interception) 2019/9/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: Mims beats defender to put Baylor on the board
videos.description: Denzel Mims puts his Iowa State defender off balance and catches a nine-yard touchdown pass from Charlie Brewer, putting Baylor up 7-0.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Mims beats defender to put Baylor on the board) 2019/9/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: Mims catches 2nd TD of the day
videos.description: Denzel Mims catches a 24-yard touchdown pass from Charlie Brewer to put Baylor up 13-0.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Mims catches 2nd TD of the day) 2019/9/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: Kolar dives into end zone to put Iowa State on top
videos.description: Charlie Kolar's 20-yard reception from Brock Purdy puts Iowa State up 21-20, after entering the fourth quarter down 20 to Baylor.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Kolar dives into end zone to put Iowa State on top) 2019/9/28 ESHEET
